ht is 3500K to 4500K and daylight white light is over 5000K.<br>Here we rec=
ommend our article on <a href=3D"https://www.emilum.com/blog/wissen/cct-led=
-anpassbares-weisslicht/">CCT LED</a>, as it not only explains CCT in detai=
